{
  "sn22.126:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 ",
  "sn22.126:0.2": "13. Avijjāvagga ",
  "sn22.126:0.3": "126. Samudayadhammasutta ",
  "sn22.126:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
  "sn22.126:1.2": "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā …pe… ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
  "sn22.126:1.3": "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. ",
  "sn22.126:1.4": "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā; ",
  "sn22.126:1.5": "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti? ",
  "sn22.126:2.1": "“Idha, bhikkhu, assutavā puthujjano samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.2": "vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.3": "samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:2.4": "Samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.5": "vayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘vayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.6": "samudayavayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:2.7": "Samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ …pe… ",
  "sn22.126:2.8": "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.9": "vayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.10": "samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:2.11": "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.12": "vayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:2.13": "samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:2.14": "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā; ",
  "sn22.126:2.15": "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti. ",
  "sn22.126:3.1": "Evaṃ vutte, so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
  "sn22.126:3.2": "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. ",
  "sn22.126:3.3": "Katamā nu kho, bhante, vijjā; ",
  "sn22.126:3.4": "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti? ",
  "sn22.126:4.1": "“Idha, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.2": "vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.3": "samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:4.4": "Samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.5": "vayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘vayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.6": "samudayavayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammā vedanā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:4.7": "Samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ … ",
  "sn22.126:4.8": "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.9": "vayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.10": "samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:4.11": "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.12": "vayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘vayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; ",
  "sn22.126:4.13": "samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. ",
  "sn22.126:4.14": "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, vijjā; ",
  "sn22.126:4.15": "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti. ",
  "sn22.126:4.16": "Paṭhamaṃ. "
}